# Client (Vite) build-time config.
#
# Same-origin hosting (Express serves the built client): leave this UNSET — API calls
# stay relative ("/api/...").
#
# Split hosting (Cloudflare Pages front end + separate backend on a VPS): set this to the
# backend's PUBLIC origin so the built site calls the VPS. No trailing slash, no "/api".
# In Cloudflare Pages, set the same variable under Settings -> Environment variables.
#
# VITE_API_BASE_URL=https://api.sqlmastery.example.com
